lead_paragraph: Maddie Manning scored 17 points with three 3-pointers and a career-high 10 steals and No. 20 Oklahoma overcame poor first-half shooting to rally for a 74-60 win over Portland State on Wednesday night at the Puerto Rico Classic.

headline.print_headline: No 20 Oklahoma Women Beat Portland State 74-60
